Co-Founder, Familylifers.com, a social media platform, Pastor Bisi Adewale, has said the new platform would enhance wealth creation, eliminate unemployment, provide employment opportunities and ultimately reduce crime rates in the society. He spoke during the launch of the online platform, at Sheraton Hotels, Ikeja, Lagos. He said: “The thoughts of helping solve many of our nation’s problems were the propelling force behind creating this website and its applications. The platform will help in wealth creation and eliminate unemployment as the platform will provide employment opportunities.” The platform will also empower young people and families. It will keep the youth busy and reduce crime rates. It will help parents in raising better children for society.”